## [1] 2.875658
HPDgrid <- function(prob,level=0.95){
  prob.sort=sort(prob,decreasing = T)
  M=min(which(cumsum(prob.sort)>=level))
  height=prob.sort[M]
  HPD.index=which(prob>=height)
  HPD.level=sum(prob[HPD.index])
  res=list(index=HPD.index, level=HPD.level)
  return(res)
}
